OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWidespread early low cloud,
OL,6,Fmist and fog likely slowly clearing to
OL,7,Fleave a dry, mild and generally bright
OL,8,Fafternoon. Cloud thickening into the
OL,9,Fevening however, bringing a threat of
OL,10,Frain for the north and west to end the
OL,11,Fday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain spreading slowly east to
OL,14,Fall areas overnight into Friday
OL,15,Fmorning. Turning cooler with an
OL,16,Fincreasing risk of sleet or snow over
OL,17,Fhigher ground of the Pennines.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
