OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FEarly rain easing into Friday
OL,6,Fafternoon, cloud perhaps breaking to
OL,7,Fgiving some afternoon brightness, but
OL,8,Frain returns into the evening. Feeling
OL,9,Fmuch cooler by day under widespread
OL,10,Fcloud.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,13,Fdrier day likely Saturday, with some
OL,14,Fbrightness after a locally cool start.
OL,15,FConditions becoming cloudier and
OL,16,Fmilder into Sunday and Monday, with
OL,17,Flow cloud, fog and some rain returning.
